tsp-trustbadge (React TrustBadge component for the Trust Standard Protocol)
Copyright © 2026 LexiCo AS, Norway

This product includes software developed at LexiCo AS. TrustBadge is the
end-user receipt component for the Trust Standard Protocol
(github.com/Lexi-TSP/Trust-Standard-Protocol, Apache-2.0). It renders fields
from a verified TrustEnvelope; verification is provided by the consumer (pair
with tsp-verify, Apache-2.0). Conformance of the envelope schema is defined by
the fixtures of github.com/Lexi-TSP/tsp-spec.

